Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================OP============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.84,0:01:28.83,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}茫茫人海行色匆匆　擦肩而过碰撞纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.03,0:01:34.95,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}感受彼此羽翼的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:41.14,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}用寂寞抱紧你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.73,0:01:47.59,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}无须其他任何表示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:50.96,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}等候交融的瞬间　觉醒的永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:54.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}心急如焚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:02:00.54,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}时光荏苒转瞬即逝　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.71,0:02:10.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}只能叹息　心愿遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:16.31,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}炽热的灵魂　传递真情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:19.51,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}不再有保留
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:25.86,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}你曾经的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:31.14,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}又在何方…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:11.85,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,1500)\an3}曾如此形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:20.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,2500)\an3}黄昏却已变色…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:37.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}平凡的温柔　让你远去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:45.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}被抛弃的心灵　四处彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:53.24,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}这份失落　如果就是生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}我愿在夜空下　从此闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:06.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾形影不离　黄昏却已变色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:17.77,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}{\be1}至少让我在月光下　静静入眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人是纳斯卡级2 Ginn3
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 神盾也在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爸爸的船呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.73,0:00:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去跟他们说 敢攻击爸爸的船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.67,0:00:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就去！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是地球联合军战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰正保护
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PLANT最高议会议长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:00:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西格尔·克莱茵之女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.76,0:01:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:39.62,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1174,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}分歧点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 全军停止攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听见刚才的广播吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿救来的平民作人质
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那种卑鄙的家伙为伍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的正义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.56,0:02:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会救出她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前危机暂且过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但情况没任何根本性改善呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可利用这段时间重振旗鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当前情况下 这十分重要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧哦 这还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了老大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这船还真是灾星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是克鲁泽吧 真要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿那女孩做人质要挟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后夹着尾巴溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军原来是这样的军队？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是因为我们不中用？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论你还是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没资格指责舰长和大副她们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算继续跟随下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝大人只要还在他们手里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且他们打算与月球舰队会合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 又不能眼睁睁地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看拉克丝大人被舰队带走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莫夫在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多久能与我们会合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当前位置在6.509 Y0.3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会合至少还要7小时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样在我们行动之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就会与大部队会合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的船呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的船呢 它怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾 芙蕾！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说「会没事的」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说「我们也去 会没事的」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没保住爸爸的船？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没把他们都干掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾 基拉很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 因为自己也是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没尽全力战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 把爸爸还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿救来的平民当人质
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这种卑鄙的家伙为伍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的正义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是因为我们不中用？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 因为自己也是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没有尽全力战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国防委员会 萨拉委员长来电
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 我马上来舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了个丫头 兴师动众
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外出散步 听到这里传来声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过 不可以随便走动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被当作间谍的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这只小粉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别喜欢散步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更准确的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要被锁住 它一定会打开门出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不承认！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我们回去吧 来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗已经结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你却似乎愁眉不展
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实并不想去打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰是很好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰·萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是那台机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神盾的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和他都是善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是件悲哀的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也认识阿斯兰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰·萨拉是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我未来的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然人很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却非常沉默寡言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这只哈罗就是他送我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉他说我非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他第二次又送来了哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 阿斯兰他一点也没变
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我的机械鸟特里也是他做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 要是不用战斗就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然能理解芙蕾的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那也太过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为自己也是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:10:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没有尽全力战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉每次都有拼尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看在眼里的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也不是怀疑他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舰桥工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶机动战士有多辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不知道也难
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 真的是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 卡兹？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架被抢走的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神盾什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶它的人 好像是基拉以前的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我听见他跟那个调整人女孩说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是以前的好朋友」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰·萨拉是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我未来的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这样下去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 加油加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是基拉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说话 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是在干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想带她去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你们别声张好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想把你们卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再这样下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 抓女孩做人质
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是坏人才干的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,套在外面…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 怎么突然就几个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机会再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就难说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 你会回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到我们这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中士！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请离开这里 我要打开舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要回来 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭 你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子带着小姐走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.25,0:15:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 气压阀已经被打开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走 请抓好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认长腿放出机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一级战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士乘员立即准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 机动战士乘员…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是地球联合军
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号所属机动战士 强袭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,携带并准备移交拉克丝·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 条件是纳斯卡级停船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神盾驾驶员独自前来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果违反条件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不保证她的生命安全
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葫芦里卖的什么药 长腿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 请让我去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的目的还不确定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝大人是否真的搭乘…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 允许你去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可否认是一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方的驾驶员看来也血气方刚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停船 把我的Cgue准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 那是他自作主张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请下令攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次强袭就会变成敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳斯卡级引擎停止 正在制动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神盾接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿斯兰·萨拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开驾驶舱！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么远看不清 让他知道是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就把她带走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:18:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的照顾 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰 也感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 你也一起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么理由要留在地球军？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实 也不想和你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那艘船上有我要保护的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朋友在！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:20:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次战斗时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会向你开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.21,0:20:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人机动战士正在离开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎启动 阿迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰机动战士出击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳斯卡级引擎启动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道要来这套
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰带拉克丝小姐返航
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉戈上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为他们会什么都不做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:20:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:20:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险别乱碰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳·卢·克鲁泽队长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把我这个追悼团代表所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成战场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 说话也不分清场合
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做绝不会被允许
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请立即停止战斗行为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个让人头疼的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 拉克丝·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不承认 绝不承认
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么回事 咱们也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上去碰得灰头土脸也没什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:21:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个了不得的公主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.56,0:22:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想 就这么算了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.10,0:23:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失在虚空中的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及 逝去的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么才是无法挽回的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同动机的言语静静地沉淀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.11,0:23:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将基拉困住
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.88,0:23:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当明白自己被赋予的使命时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破茧而出的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.53,0:23:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达SEED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.20,0:23:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「觉醒之刃」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.76,0:23:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在驰骋的天际中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.06,0:23:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会发现什么 高达






